body:
Job profile:
Temenos is extending its portfolio with new products. We are looking to extend our team in Bucharest with several Java developers who can implement a new web solution using standard and proprietary technologies. 

What you'll be doing:
•	Solution design and implementation;
•	Implement layouts and business logic using a proprietary UX platform;
•	Communicate with the business team and validate requirements;
•	Work in a global team, collaborate with peers, managers and testers;
•	Maintain technical documentation when required.

Requirements:
•	Experience in developing Web solutions;
•	Technical knowledge:
o	Java
o	Web services 
o	HTML, CSS, JavaScript;
•	Experience in producing technical specifications;
•	Nice to have experience of cookies, capturing/tracking Id and device information, Rules engines;
•	Nice to have experience of web development for Campaign Management, Content Targeting, Decisioning Platforms, Financial Services and/or Banking software;
•	Very good command of the English language;
•	Strong ability to look at problems from user, designer and developer point of view;
•	Ability to meet deadlines, proactive;
•	Team player attitude and attention to details.

Offer (benefits):
•	Motivating salary;
•	Meal tickets;
•	Medical insurance;
•	Massage sessions;
•	Relaxation room (pool table/ ping pong, board games);
•	25 days Annual Vacation.
